{"tid":1807374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日經 仲撚緊狗既人唔該思考吓「撚狗」既原意","createTime":"2020-01-01T18:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T19:06:30.000Z","uid":161781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e257055ee2ea191257819213f7bdd5ceab10bc6a","tid":1807374,"uid":161781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:56:18.000Z","msg":"雖然連登大部分人都知屌狗係不可取，但都想講吓<br />\n記唔記得「撚狗」個term一開始係點誕生？<br />\n係形容係黃大仙等等社區利用街坊身分同衣著去屌狗既行為，當時大家都話好係因為咁樣風險低但同時達到效果<br />\n而家出到港島、尖沙咀仲破口大罵，果D只叫「屌狗」/「引狗咬」，高風效但低回報，完全唔係當初遊刃有餘既「撚狗」"},{"pid":"8da865d5c913d5cea8f79f447031800050dcd02c","tid":1807374,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:59:27.000Z","msg":"【旺角狗倒地真相！！】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1807368\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1807368</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"84a78024f130013ceba274e8c0ff36a5fcacea1e","tid":1807374,"uid":161781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T19:06:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}